<div class="main-tab-content">
  <div class="tab-col-left">
    <h2>In the Moment</h2>
    <p>I read a book recently on collective wisdom and there was a lot of talk about peoples human need to take stance. This only helped me as I was designing this interface.<br><br> I realize there are micro-blogs, social networks and news sites for people to declare things, but no place really dedicated to building a profile of positions, where people can show their true character based on their beliefs. Not just religious beliefs, but all beliefs.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-col-mid">
    <div class="tab-bullets">
      <p class="title">Goals</p>
      <ul>
        <li><span>Create a place for people to take stance</span></li>
        <li><span>This is NOT a question and answering service</span></li>
        <li><span>Let people build profiles based on their positions on verified statements</span></li>
        <li><span>Build a place where religionists and atheists can find common ground. Hahaha.</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="title">Overview</p>
      <p>People like taking stance. I'm not sure if there is a place on the internet today where we can build a profile of stances on issues. This would be a great place for people to sort their differences.</p>
      <div class="home-slideshow slideshow-seven">
        <div><%= image_tag "layout/marketing_portal/slide_rtwo_1.jpg", :alt => "" %></div>
        <div><%= image_tag "layout/marketing_portal/slide_rtwo_2.jpg", :alt => "" %></div>
        <div><%= image_tag "layout/marketing_portal/slide_rtwo_3.jpg", :alt => "" %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
      <div id="home_slide_nav7" class="home_slide_nav"></div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-col-right"></div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
<%= javascript_tag do -%>
$(document).ready(function(){
  var rand = $('.slideshow-seven > div').length;
  $('.slideshow-seven').cycle({
    pager: '#home_slide_nav7',
    cleartype: 1,
    timeout:0,
    startingSlide: Math.floor(Math.random() * rand),
    fx: 'none'
  });
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").css({opacity: 0, visibility: "visible"});
  var html = $(".hidden-media-widget").html();
  $(".hidden-media-widget").remove();
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").html(html);
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").css({opacity: 0, visibility: "visible"}).animate({opacity: 1}, 1000);
  $(".mast-text-black").hide();
  $(".mast-text-black").slideDown("slow");
});
<% end -%>

